name: Finnish Baltic Sea benthic monitoring, POHJE database
description: The POHJE database includes data on benthic macrofauna,covering the Finnishcoastal areas as well as the offshoreareas of the BalticSea. The quantitative data mainly stem from theFinnish national monitoring program and statutory monitoring programs, but alsodata from surveys and research projects areincluded. In total the databasecontain aproximately 100 000 quantitativerecords including developmental stages, with a time spanfrom 1965 to present. The databaseis regularly maintained and datais added continuously.
